civic services, the means to use data to uphold \u2018rule of law\u2019, vote and participate in civics or the array of other examples in which we have the technology, but not the accessible application in which to apply the use of our technology to social/human needs.\xA0\xA0"), mdx("p", null, "Indeed the works we produce and contribute on the web are for the most-part provided not simply freely, but at our own cost. \xA0 The things that are \u2018human\u2019 are less important and indeed, poorly supported.**"));
